Evaluation du troisieme projet routier - Rwanda

abstracts.cdata!:
The Third Highway Project will provide
            for the improvement to paved standard of the
            Ruhengeri-Gisenyi road (about 60 km); feasibility study and
            detailed engineering of the Kigali-Ruhengeri-Cyanika road;
            technical assistance, and training of DRB highway
            maintenance personnel.
